ANONYMOUS, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. CURTIS PUBLISHING COMPANY, Defendant-Appellee. No. 6. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 5, 1934. Showers, Jason & Quinn, of New York City (Peter W. Quinn, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Carter, Ledyard & Milburn, of Now York City (J. M. Richardson Lyeth, of Now York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before MANTON, AUGUSTUS N. HAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed.
